'''''Munyurangabo''''' ni filime yo mu 2007 iyobowe na Lee Isaac Chung . Ifata amashusho yose mu Rwanda hamwe nabakinnyi baho, niyo filime yambere yerekana inkuru mururimi rw' [[Ikinyarwanda|iKinyarwanda.]]  Yerekanwe bwa mbere  mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 2007 ku ya 24 Gicurasi  kandi yegukana igihembo kinini muri AFI Fest 2007.  Umunyamerika Roger Ebert ayita filime nziza kandi ikomeye ." 

