== Umusaruro ==
Nk’uko ikinyamakuru ''The New York Times kibitangaza ngo'' mbere yo gukora iyi filime, umugore wa Diregiteri Lee Isaac Chung, Valerie, umuvuzi w’ubuhanzi, yari yagiye mu Rwanda nk'umukorerabushake wo gukorana n’abagize ingaruka kuri jenoside yo mu 1994. Abimusabye, Chung yamuherekeje mu Rwanda kandi yitangira kwigisha ishuri ryo gukina amafirime mu kigo cy’ubutabazi i [[Kigali]] mu mpeshyi ya 2006. Chung abonye umwanya wo kwerekana ukuri kwiki gihe cyu [[Rwanda]] no guha abanyeshuri be imyitozo ngororamubiri ifatika, Chung yahageze afite igitabo k'impapuro icyenda yari yanditse abifashijwemo n'inshuti  (ndetse amaherezo nabafatanyabikorwa ba firime hamwe nabandi banditsi) ) Samuel Gray Anderson. Chung yafashe amashusho ya Munyurangabo mu minsi 11, akorana n'itsinda ry'abakinnyi badafite umwuga Chung yasanze mu bigo by'imfubyi byaho ndetse n'abanyeshuri be nk'abakozi. 

== Iterambere ryakurikiyeho ==
Lee Isaac Chung akomeje gutoza abasore bakora amafilime yo mu [[Rwanda]] abinyujije muri Almond Tree Rwanda, ikigo cy’u [[Rwanda]] cy’isosiyete ikora ibicuruzwa ikorera muri Amerika,. {{RefFCAT|556}}

